ENGAGE YOUR AUDIENCE

INTERACTIVE SHOWS WITH THE WORLD’S SAFEST DRONES

ENGAGE YOUR AUDIENCE

INTERACTIVE SHOWS WITH  THE WORLD’S SAFEST DRONES

ENGAGE YOUR AUDIENCE

INTERACTIVE SHOWS WITH  THE WORLD’S SAFEST DRONES

WOW YOUR AUDIENCE!

   The turnkey solution for events of every size – with monetizable and
   interactive shows:

ATTRACTING ATTENTION: 97% of audience recalls it after the event

SHAREABLE: Boost social media activity by up to 500%

INTERACTIVE: People are interacting during 96% of the show

CUSTOMIZABLE: Get your own design into the air

SAFE: You can safely touch it in flight

   Want to learn more? Get in touch with us!

   IFRAME:
   http://www.youtube.com/embed/xxujTYpxtwo?wmode=transparent&autoplay=0

VALUE

FOR AUDIENCES

   Fun and interactive experience, for instance a flying selfie drone.
   Experience a bird’s-eye perspective of the event and spot yourself in
   the live video! Built-in lights add another fascination on top of the
   magically smooth flight!

FOR ORGANIZERS

   Discover entirely new ways to connect with your audience! Unique and
   interactive entertainment pulls people to your event. Monetize by
   including branded activation into a sponsorship package.

FOR SPONSORS

   Leverage sponsoring packages by boosting brand awareness and recall at
   live events. We bring your design airborne (any shape possible with
   full 360° digital color print) and allow you to connect to your
   audience!

MARKETS

EXPERIENTIAL ADVERTISING

   Not only can we customize our spheres to the customers needs with 360°
   prints, we can virtually bring any object in the air, resulting in very
   effective* marketing.
   *We could measure an increase in social media activity of up to 500% as
   well as tremendous recall.

SPORTS

   When there is no game going on, AEROTAIN entertains the crowd with live
   video interaction, for instance a flying Kiss-Cam. Besides pulling
   people to the event, sponsor’s logos can be placed on both video
   content and the hull, allowing to leverage sponsorship packages or
   creating new revenue streams.

CULTURAL EVENTS

   Be it for conferences, exhibitions or concerts. With our fleet of
   innovative flying objects we add interaction and entertainment from the
   third dimension to the event.

CORPORATE EVENTS

   Need some eye-candy for your corporate event? Something that makes
   people wonder and fosters discussions? AEROTAIN can do it!

BROADCASTING

   Wherever there is a video production going on, AEROTAIN allows to get a
   bird’s-eye view in a safe way. Flight times of multiple hours and live
   Full HD stream also allow for live productions.

